cs press, 2001.</p>\n<a href=\"#fnref-2\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a>\n</li>\n<li id=\"fn-3\">\n<p>Carr, Daniel B., et al. <a href=\"https://www.jstor.org/stable/2289444\">\"Scatterplot matrix techniques for large N.\"</a> <em>Journal of the American Statistical Association</em> 82.398 (1987): 424-436.</p>\n<a href=\"#fnref-3\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>","excerpt":"is a visualization method for showing the distribution of two variables along the horizontal and vertical axes. Scatter plots are used to…","overview":"<p>is a visualization method for showing the distribution of two variables along the horizontal and vertical axes. Scatter plots are used to…</p>","fields":{"variationOf":null},"frontmatter":{"title":"scatter plot","synonyms":["scatter graph","scatter chart","scattergram","scatter diagram"],"functions":["distribution","correlation"],"visualizationTechniques":[{"techniqueId":"AXI","informationType":"quantity","axisDirection":"horizontal"},{"techniqueId":"AXI","informationType":"quantity","axisDirection":"vertical"}],"informationTypes":null,"axisDirections":null,"examples":[{"title":"Sound Effects - Productivity in Offices","link":"https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2019/10/24/why-open-plan-offices-get-a-bad-rap","note":null,"image":"noise-level-in-offices-economist.png"},{"title":"Greying of The Nobel Laureates","link":"https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2016/10/03/greying-of-the-nobel-laureates","note":null,"image":"age-of-nobel-prize-winners.png"},{"title":"1,780 Habitable Exoplanets, 2014","link":"https://web.archive.org/web/20140822200552/http://news.nationalgeographic.com:80/news/2014/04/140417-exoplanet-interactive/","note":"This is an example of one dimensional scatter plot","image":"habitable-exoplanets-asof-2014.png"}],"tools":[{"name":"Adobe Illustrator","link":"https://helpx.adobe.com/illustrator/using/graphs.html"},{"name":"PowerPoint","link":"https://products.office.com/en/powerpoint"},{"name":"Appl